    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-07-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-07-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="325"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d325">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Perry</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 14.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-07-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 27, 1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> Your despatch No. 72, of June 24, has been
                    received. In it you announce that his Highness the Bey, having determined to
                    send hither an envoy for the purpose of presenting his portrait and his
                    felicitations to the government of the United States on the abolition of slavery
                    and the restoration of peace, had expressed the desire that you should accompany
                    his envoy. The leave of absence which you ask for that purpose is hereby
                    granted.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Amos Perry,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c., Tunis.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
